### FnCast Minimal API Requests (VS Code REST Client)
# Requires the 'REST Client' extension by Huachao Mao.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5097

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Ingest (text/plain)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payload": "hello world",
  "contentType": "text/plain"
}

### Ingest (application/json)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payload": "{\"correlationId\":\"abc123\",\"source\":\"demo\"}",
  "contentType": "application/json"
}

### Switch to Docker port
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Health (Docker)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
